籤詩版本二:
Osisi pine na osisi cypress na-eto nke ọma, na mmiri ozuzo, snow, ifufe, na ntu oyi bụ ihe niile a ga-eme.
Ọdịnihu ga-abụ ihe dị ukwuu na mberede, ama ama ga-abụkwa ogidi.
詩意:
Hexagram a bụ onyinyo nke oke ọhịa nke pine na cypresses.
Enwere onye isi n'ihe niile.
解曰: Jisie n'ụzọ. Ọrụ bara uru ogologo ndụ. Ugbo silkworm chara acha. Ezinụlọ ahụ bara ọgaranya.
籤詩故事一:
◇Fan Wenzheng ama ebiere nditan̄ nnyụn̄ nse porridge
Fan Zhongyan, onye ọchịchị a ma ama na usoro ndị eze Song, si n'ezinụlọ dara ogbenye mgbe ọ bụ nwata, ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ n'ụlọ ndị mọnk nke dị n'ugwu Changbai, na-esi nri porridge na lita abụọ nke millet kwa ụbọchị, mgbe ọ gbasiri ike n'otu abalị, ọ na-egbutu ya. were mma rie iberibe anọ, rie iberibe abua n'ututu na anyasi, b͕ue ufọdu nime ya ka ọ rie.
A na-eji nke a kọwaa onye na-adịghị atụ egwu ihe isi ike, na-amụsi ike, na-emecha ghọọ talent nke nnukwu uru.
Beechapụ harrow wee see porridge
聖意: Jiazhai dị mma maka onwe ya, na-achọ akụ na ụba, udo, azụmahịa, alụmdi na nwunye, ịga nke ọma, Liujia, ndị nwoke na-agafe agafe, ubi ntụkwasị obi, silkworms, anụ ụlọ isii, mmebi, ịchụ ndị mmadụ, ikpe, ịkwaga, ihe onwunwe furu efu, ọrịa, ili Anshan, ihe ọma
古人: Fan Wenzheng kpebiri ịkatọ na ise porridge
